details.description: Ready-made holes for easy assembly of the legs Restraints can be placed in the center of the room The table is stable even on a floor that is not straight thanks to the adjustable legs thanks to the finish in the back of drawers that prevent excessive pulling
details.good_to_know: Including screws for fixing the legs to the table surface, including plastic shields for home use. This product creates and tests the top surface of the table in place.
